{"tid":2456342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖）係黨鐵見過咩大陸閪既行為","createTime":"2021-03-22T00:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T05:25:38.000Z","uid":339908,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1ebda00bbf92e9e6133cd7355ec4c013fdba348a","tid":2456342,"uid":339908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T00:30:51.000Z","msg":"香港人最早返工，咩車都咁多人<br />\n逼，我明<br />\n但依條撚樣 隻手好似小兒麻痹咁<br />\n係咁撞，撞撚到我同佢後面個位先生<br />\n我同後面個個先生係咁啤住佢都算，<br />\n因為我地企正電視底<br />\n條八婆竟然轉身去睇電視<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最撚仆街既係，去到美孚<br />\n多人落左車 咁岩比佢見到有位<br />\n佢用the flash 既速度坐左落去<br />\n<br />\n佢當前面個伯伯同婆婆 唔係人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xgNv5Wi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxgNv5Wi.png&h=1a1defbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68a593b0053a6c3ff24aa60d766c0c0749d0c887","tid":2456342,"uid":31237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T00:32:02.000Z","msg":"四個人位 迫到變五個"},{"pid":"c72a829af1b5d26f4d418d66ebed98061e147894","tid":2456342,"uid":59114,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T00:34:02.000Z","msg":"好正常。黨鐵唔係比大陸人搭架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b58ce1fa5c02e6b5c28b248d32cf5aad420ffd2","tid":2456342,"uid":254813,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T00:34:46.000Z","msg":"唔當場屌9佢？齋啤住佢同係度post有咩用？佢又唔知，勇敢d啦香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41001d66b243e2891f28a49feafc491fd5285cd1","tid":2456342,"uid":274432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T00:37:50.000Z","msg":"踢9條臭西喇"},{"pid":"5d831fbd22559446bc4095168bca3877e0aea4a9","tid":2456342,"uid":43369,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-